  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Ultimate Off-Road Experience In VR - Face the challenges of harsh weather and terrain in fully immersive VR for the first time! Tackle treacherous mud, fierce rivers, rocky paths, and more, to reach your goals.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3188340/extras/4702582cd493fe2c08618013258e65fa.poster.avif?t=1729753646\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3188340/extras/4702582cd493fe2c08618013258e65fa.webm?t=1729753646\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3188340/extras/4702582cd493fe2c08618013258e65fa.mp4?t=1729753646\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >8 Unique All-Terrain Vehicles - Vary your playstyle by stepping into 8 unique vehicles, each with distinct attributes, including flatbeds, repair modules, log carriers and more!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3188340/extras/666556547a08ecdba1c3e826c597ab6e.poster.avif?t=1729753646\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3188340/extras/666556547a08ecdba1c3e826c597ab6e.webm?t=1729753646\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3188340/extras/666556547a08ecdba1c3e826c597ab6e.mp4?t=1729753646\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore Immersive Environments - Adventure across vast landscapes in either story or free-play mode and discover new environments through extreme and unpredictable conditions.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3188340/extras/88d326bd56b8e2427a83c1741e844683.poster.avif?t=1729753646\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3188340/extras/88d326bd56b8e2427a83c1741e844683.webm?t=1729753646\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3188340/extras/88d326bd56b8e2427a83c1741e844683.mp4?t=1729753646\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Interact With Your Vehicle’s Cockpit - Strategically use your tablet, gear shifter, windshield wipers and more to assist in your missions.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3188340/extras/771ddbca1f3d514544a46bf2628f3427.poster.avif?t=1729753646\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3188340/extras/771ddbca1f3d514544a46bf2628f3427.webm?t=1729753646\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3188340/extras/771ddbca1f3d514544a46bf2628f3427.mp4?t=1729753646\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The Ultimate Off-Road Experience In VR - Face the challenges of harsh weather and terrain in fully immersive VR for the first time! Tackle treacherous mud, fierce rivers, rocky paths, and more, to reach your goals.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3188340/extras/4702582cd493fe2c08618013258e65fa.poster.avif?t=1729753646\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3188340/extras/4702582cd493fe2c08618013258e65fa.webm?t=1729753646\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3188340/extras/4702582cd493fe2c08618013258e65fa.mp4?t=1729753646\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >8 Unique All-Terrain Vehicles - Vary your playstyle by stepping into 8 unique vehicles, each with distinct attributes, including flatbeds, repair modules, log carriers and more!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3188340/extras/666556547a08ecdba1c3e826c597ab6e.poster.avif?t=1729753646\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3188340/extras/666556547a08ecdba1c3e826c597ab6e.webm?t=1729753646\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3188340/extras/666556547a08ecdba1c3e826c597ab6e.mp4?t=1729753646\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore Immersive Environments - Adventure across vast landscapes in either story or free-play mode and discover new environments through extreme and unpredictable conditions.</p><p class=\"bb_paragr